      <!-- Color -->
      <section class="section" id="color">
        <p class="eyebrow">02 — Color</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Color <a class="anchor" href="#color" aria-label="Copy link to section">#</a></h2>
        <p class="lede">The Tailored Applications color system — the core brand colors, their full tint and shade scales, an extended palette for interfaces, and the brand gradients. Every value is click-to-copy.</p>

        <div class="part">
          <span class="part-num">Section 1</span>
          <h3 class="part-title">Core palette</h3>
        </div>

        <p class="subhead">Primary colors</p>
        <p class="note">The four colors the brand is built on. Each lists HEX, RGB, and CMYK — click to copy the HEX.</p>
