          <span class="part-num">Section 4</span>
          <h3 class="part-title">Bilingual system</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="note">One family across two scripts. English sets in Latin, left-aligned (LTR); Central Kurdish and Arabic set in IBM Plex Sans Arabic, right-aligned (RTL). Mirror the alignment and keep weight and rhythm consistent across both.</p>
